Class MoveEvent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MoveEvent
extends java.awt.AWTEvent
    A MoveEvent extends AWTEvent by exposing a constructor that take a Point source. This allows the consumer of the event to know what Point was clicked.
